      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "GOT A SETTING (7) proved too good on debut over 320m at this track to score by 2.5 lengths (18.41). Drawn wide but has good early pace. Can make it back to back wins. Can continue winning ways. TIGER BELL (1) is not the most reliable at box rise. Last start finished 4th on June 5 over 320m at this track behind Let's Go Jill beaten 5.5 lengths (18.76) in a Grade 5. Can hit the frame with the right run. FAITHFUL FLYER (2) comes off an average performance last start when seventh at Nowra over 365m behind Nordic Shiraz (23.04) in a Grade 5. Should be about the money. MAGNIFICENT (8) is worth a look over a shorter distance this time.",
